title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: You may be intrigued by an innovative technology and cant wait to get your hands on the newest cell phone, computer, or camera. Youre curious and hungry for the novelty that any invention brings. But youre also looking to release pent-up pressures and this form of retail therapy might satisfy you as well as any other. However, your gratification depends on the reason youre willing to part with your money. If you want to be ahead of the curve for the sake of your ego, then be certain youre purchasing something so unique that no other time will do but now. Be a trendsetter, not just trendy.
